title: Ravage Machinery - Subordinates Of The Mechanism 2015 a4k
description:
Northern Finland death/thrash metal act Ravage Machinery has announced their full-length debut album Subordinates Of The Mechanism.

Subordinates Of The Mechanism was forged by Drop Hammer Studios (Torture Killer, Hateform) and mastered by Jens Bogren ( At The Gates, Arch Enemy, Amon Amarth). The album will be released on April 24th by One Man Army.




Country: Finland

Genre: Death / Thrash Metal

Quality: mp3, CBR 192 kbps
